Dollar Falls Versus Euro After S&P Puts U.S. on Review for Possible Cut

-- B y   C a n d i c e   Z a c h a r i a h s
-- 
2011-07-14T23:43:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-14/dollar-falls-versus-euro-after-s-p-puts-u-s-on-review-for-possible-cut.html
The dollar declined against the
euro, yen and swiss franc after  Standard & Poor’s  put the U.S.’s
AAA rating on review for a possible downgrade.  The greenback slid to $1.4194 as of 8:42 a.m. in  Tokyo  from
$1.4143 yesterday in  New York . It fell 0.3 percent to 78.92 yen
and weakened 0.5 percent versus the Swiss franc to 81.23
centimes.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Candice Zachariahs in Sydney at 
 czachariahs2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
